Thousands of people have asked me, “How could Ronald not recognize sewage Joe”? A few reasons.  Day one I heard he loved parks and rec so I stayed in his blind spot.  I didn’t say much.  Pat McCurdy was a little prickly and I didn’t send him any dick pics from sanitation.  Which was hard.  The largest battle was not talking to him. We are both 6’5” and from San Diego.  @sunnyg_sd is still as sweet as when I met him. He just has more followers on Instagram than me now.  Thanks for watching #juryduty on @amazonfreevee —- everyone involved was amazing and it was fun to gain 25 pounds. And yes, my C4 and C5 are still compacted and impacted and constantly moving.  Love, Pat.

This was the best part of my European vacation.  @seguratom and @shaunnixphotography agreed to join me on my daily mile swim in the freezing water of Athens.  It was something very cold in Celsius.  Colder in Fahrenheit.  37 degrees.  After half a mile Tom and Shaun couldn’t make it back to the dock so I allowed them to attach to me like remora. Remora is not a parasite surprisingly despite being attached to the host.  Me.  Instead, they are considered to have a commensal relationship with their host, since they do not hurt the host and are along for the ride.  Once we were safely on the dock Shaun and I quickly attached ourselves to Tom again and he continued to feed us and fly us around Europe.  Thanks, Tom.  #remora

A few jokes in Paris.  They liked that the stage looked like my hotel room.  Jacket on the floor.  I was telling them about the bolt I took off that tall tower.  Thank you @seguratom for the honeymoon my wife wanted.  And yes, I am the mysterious juror #1 from #juryduty in @amazonfreevee ‘s number 1 show in the world.  Love, Pat McCurdy.
